## 🌐 6. Publishing to GitHub

Once your folders and docs are ready:

```bash
cd D:\Tennis
git init tennis-ml-insights
cd tennis-ml-insights
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit - tennis ML insights project"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/<yourusername>/tennis-ml-insights.git
git push -u origin main
